  "logic": "Finite, two-valued propositional semantics with exhaustive valuation enumeration in independent bounded modules.",
  "scope_notice": "This study-local kernel encodes selected Boolean consequences and counterexample obligations from FMO-0.1. It omits quantified unbounded domains, full transition traces, natural-language claim interpretation, distributed concurrency, policy composition, external systems, and physical deletion. A satisfying kernel model, an entailment, or a retained countermodel does not prove, validate, or establish the consistency of all FMO-0.1.",
